trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **NavigationFailed** event.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 **NavigationFailed** 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: These event arguments contain information about a navigation that failed, and are passed to handlers of the **NavigationFailed** event, which is implemented by the following: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> NavigationFailedEventArgs encapsulates the following details of the failed navigation request: - **Navigation Initiation**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 실패, 처리기로 전달 하는 탐색에 대 한 정보를 포함 하는 이러한 이벤트 인수는 **NavigationFailed** 다음에서 구현 하는 이벤트:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>실패 한 탐색 요청의 다음 세부 정보를 캡슐화 하는 NavigationFailedEventArgs:- **탐색 시작**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Exception**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **탐색 예외**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Content**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **탐색 콘텐츠**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Details**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **탐색 세부 정보**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **탐색 상태**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Exception> that was raised as the result of a failed navigation.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.Exception>실패 한 탐색의 결과로 발생 하는.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Exception> will be either a <xref:System.Net.WebException> or an <xref:System.IO.IOException>
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception>중 하나가 됩니다는 <xref:System.Net.WebException>또는 <xref:System.IO.IOException></xref:System.IO.IOException> </xref:System.Net.WebException></xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception> that was raised as the result of a failed navigation.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception>실패 한 탐색의 결과로 발생 하는.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Gets the optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation commenced.
trans-unit.target: 선택적 데이터 가져옵니다 <xref:System.Object>탐색이 시작 될 때 전달 된.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: ExtraData can be used to pass context-specific data that is specific to a particular navigation.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData 특정 탐색에만 적용 되는 상황에 맞는 데이터 전달 데 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: ExtraData contains a reference to the object that is passed as the second argument when calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData 중 하나 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>나 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> 를 호출할 때 두 번째 인수로 전달 되는 개체에 대 한 참조를 포함 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: 그렇지 않으면 `null`합니다.

trans-unit.source: The optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation commenced.
trans-unit.target: 선택적 데이터 <xref:System.Object>탐색이 시작 될 때 전달 된.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the failed navigation exception has been handled.
trans-unit.target: 실패 한 탐색 예외가 처리 되었는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: When you handle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> to process an exception that is thrown as a result of a failed navigation, and you don't want [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to continue processing the exception, you should set the Handled property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: 처리할 때 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>실패 한 탐색 하 고 결과로 throw 되는 예외 않도록 프로세스에 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 예외 처리를 계속 하려면 Handled 속성을 설정 해야 하면 `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the exception is handled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> (default).
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>예외가 처리 됩니다. 그렇지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> (기본값).

trans-unit.source: The navigator that raised this event.
trans-unit.target: 이 이벤트를 발생 시킨 탐색기입니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that is the navigator that raised this event
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object>이 이벤트를 발생 시킨 탐색기 즉</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that could not be navigated to.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] 탐색할 수 없는 콘텐츠에 대 한 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Uri> for the content that could not be navigated to.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Uri>탐색할 수 없는 콘텐츠에 대 한.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Gets the web request that was used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 콘텐츠를 요청 하는 데 사용한 웹 요청을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a web request, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>웹 요청을 캡슐화 하는 추상 기본 클래스를 이며 프로토콜 관계가 있습니다.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol-specific state and behavior, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: 일반적인 각 프로토콜에 대 한는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] 에서 파생 된 클래스가 포함 되어 <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>프로토콜 관련 상태 및 동작을 사용 하도록 확장 포함:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `pack://` 응용 프로그램 데이터 파일을 요청 하는 구성표 (참조 [WPF 응용 프로그램 리소스, 내용 및 데이터 파일](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `http://` 웹 서버에서 파일을 요청한 구성표.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `ftp://` FTP 서버에서 파일을 요청한 구성표.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `file://` 체계를 로컬 파일을 요청 합니다.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> object that was used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> 는 지정된 콘텐츠를 요청 하는 데 사용 된 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: If navigating to an object, WebRequest is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 개체를 탐색 하는 경우 WebRequest는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the web response that was returned after attempting to download the requested the specified content.
trans-unit.target: 요청 된 다운로드 하려고 시도한 후 반환 된 웹 응답에 지정 된 콘텐츠입니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a web response, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>웹 응답을 캡슐화 하는 추상 기본 클래스를 이며 프로토콜 관계가 있습니다.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol-specific state, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: 각 일반 프로토콜에 대 한는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] 에서 파생 된 클래스가 포함 되어 <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>프로토콜 관련 상태를 사용 하도록 확장 포함:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `pack://` 응용 프로그램 데이터 파일을 요청 하는 구성표 (참조 [WPF 응용 프로그램 리소스, 내용 및 데이터 파일](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse> </xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `http://` 웹 서버에서 파일을 요청한 구성표.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `ftp://` FTP 서버에서 파일을 요청한 구성표.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] 사용 하는 `file://` 체계를 로컬 파일을 요청 합니다.</xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> that was returned after attempting to download the requested the specified content.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> 다운로드는 요청 된 후 반환 된 하는 지정된 된 콘텐츠가 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: If the navigation failed, WebResponse is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: WebResponse 탐색이 실패 하는 경우는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>합니다.
